flowchart TD
    A[Skill needs external tool] --> B{Tool already in<br/>.mcp.json?}

    B -->|Yes| C{User authenticated<br/>with this MCP?}
    C -->|Yes| D[Use MCP tools directly]
    C -->|No| E["suggest_connectors()<br/>OAuth prompt to user"]
    E --> F{User authorizes?}
    F -->|Yes| D
    F -->|No| G[Fall back to<br/>Standalone Mode]

    B -->|No| H["search_mcp_registry()<br/>keywords from category mapping"]

    H --> I{Registry has<br/>matching MCP?}

    I -->|Yes| J["suggest_connectors()<br/>Present available MCPs to user"]
    J --> K{User selects<br/>and authorizes?}
    K -->|Yes| L[Update .mcp.json<br/>with server URL]
    L --> D
    K -->|No| G

    I -->|No| M{Alternative tool<br/>in same category?}
    M -->|Yes| H
    M -->|No| G

    G --> N[Ask user for<br/>manual input instead]
